---
title: Sirloin Steak & Cheesy Roast Potato Rounds with Onion-Thyme Glaze & Rainbow Slaw
description: Tonight’s the night, so let’s fire up the grill and unleash your inner carnivore; it’s time for another perfectly cooked steak! We’ve got the king of cuts with a juicy sirloin steak, served alongside roasted potato rounds enrobed in melty Cheddar cheese and a fresh slaw. Drizzle over a herby onion glaze and dig in!
